    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7 and boil a kettle</p><p>Heat a <strong>hob-safe oven-proof casserole dish</strong> with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Bash your <strong>lemongrass</strong> with a <strong>rolling pin</strong>, remove the <strong>tough outer layers</strong> of the lemongrass and set aside for later</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>Fable pulled mushrooms</strong> and<strong> lemongrass core[s]</strong> to the dish and cook for 1-2 min or until the mushrooms are lightly browned</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1688123378369-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1688123378369-x400.jpg",
