            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the stew is cooked, discard the<strong> lemongrass core[s]</strong> and <strong>lime leaf[ves]</strong></p><p>Use two forks to gently shred apart the <strong>Fable mushrooms</strong> – this technique is known as ‘pulling’</p><p>Stir the <strong>pulled Fable mushrooms </strong>through the sauce – this is your <strong>Vietnamese-style Fable mushroom & lemongrass stew</strong></p><p>Cover and leave the stew to stand for 5 min before serving (this helps the flavours to develop and makes it easier to serve!)</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
