    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> Vietnamese-style Fable mushroom & lemongrass stew</strong>, <strong>fragrant baked rice </strong>and<strong> sugar snap peas</strong></p><p>Strip your <strong>coriander leaves</strong> from their stalks and scatter over the stew</p><p>Dig in!</p>",
